Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.00,0:08:29.31,Main,,0,0,0,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.72,0:08:33.63,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh...but, it's been a long time.\nFive years, isn't it?
