Dialogue: 0,0:25:46.32,0:25:49.60,Main,,0,0,0,,Ah, ah.  You're entirely too fast!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:49.88,0:25:52.27,Main,,0,0,0,,That's why you need help, being a virgin.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:52.58,0:25:54.61,Main,,0,0,0,,Wha... what should I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:58.73,0:25:59.62,Main,,0,0,0,,Fuji...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:00.62,0:26:01.44,Main,,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:02.00,0:26:03.57,Main,,0,0,0,,Wha... no way!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:03.92,0:26:05.58,Main,,0,0,0,,Fu... Fujisaki-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:07.31,0:26:08.34,Main,,0,0,0,,Fujisaki-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:19.00,0:26:21.80,Main,,0,0,0,,She must be really tired.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:23.37,0:26:26.49,Main,,0,0,0,,And that I was worried about losing faith...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:59.92,0:27:02.85,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm really sorry, Kubota-kun.\nMe, being...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:02.85,0:27:06.29,Main,,0,0,0,,No need to apologize, Fujisaki-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:06.81,0:27:07.83,Main,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:08.72,0:27:10.30,Main,,0,0,0,,It's nothing to worry about.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:10.30,0:27:15.41,Main,,0,0,0,,After that, I called room service and\nordered smoked salmon, an egg sandwich,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:15.41,0:27:19.78,Main,,0,0,0,,and a chicken basket.  Then, with\na full stomach, fell fast asleep!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:28.15,0:27:30.37,Main,,0,0,0,,It feels good being cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:30.66,0:27:35.36,Main,,0,0,0,,I wonder if you remember from\nJr. High, the game center near school.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:35.36,0:27:38.41,Main,,0,0,0,,It's now a pizza place, ya know?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:38.41,0:27:44.87,Main,,0,0,0,,And the mansion standing to\nthe left of it? Room 201 is my room.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:46.20,0:27:48.51,Main,,0,0,0,,Tomorrow I have a photo shoot,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:49.21,0:27:53.33,Main,,0,0,0,,so, how about the day after\ntomorrow, can you come over?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:53.94,0:27:57.66,Main,,0,0,0,,If it's okay with you,\nwe can continue from last night...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:58.04,0:28:00.52,Main,,0,0,0,,I-I'm sorry, Fujisaki-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:00.80,0:28:03.44,Main,,0,0,0,,I have night shift\nthe day after tomorrow, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:03.44,0:28:04.31,Main,,0,0,0,,You can't!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:10.35,0:28:15.00,Main,,0,0,0,,Please, if it is not the\n day after tomorrow, I can't...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:17.63,0:28:18.53,Main,,0,0,0,,Please...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:40.28,0:28:44.62,Main,,0,0,0,,Kazushi-kun, have you been\nplaying around, without resting?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:44.62,0:28:48.05,Main,,0,0,0,,While you're saying that,\nwould you quit touching me, boss?!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:48.05,0:28:50.32,Main,,0,0,0,,What's that strange cake?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:50.32,0:28:52.56,Main,,0,0,0,,"Strange" is a bit rude.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:52.56,0:28:55.27,Main,,0,0,0,,"Healthy" cake? I think I'll have some.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:58.93,0:28:59.90,Main,,0,0,0,,Kazushi.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:00.56,0:29:01.23,Main,,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:01.23,0:29:05.08,Main,,0,0,0,,"Healthy" cake is just like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:05.08,0:29:10.69,Main,,0,0,0,,Will you be satisfied by\neating it, or will you get fat?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:10.69,0:29:13.06,Main,,0,0,0,,You are always thinking for someone else.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:14.00,0:29:21.40,Main,,0,0,0,,But there are times when you\nhave to decide for yourself, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:23.80,0:29:25.86,Main,,0,0,0,,But, if you get slapped,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:25.86,0:29:27.71,Main,,0,0,0,,I'll be here to comfort you!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:25.34,0:32:26.44,Main,,0,0,0,,Kubota-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:28.62,0:32:30.40,Main,,0,0,0,,Please, come in!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:32.22,0:32:33.72,Main,,0,0,0,,Sorry to intrude.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:38.81,0:32:41.40,Main,,0,0,0,,You know,\nI have something to show you.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:52.08,0:32:53.13,Main,,0,0,0,,Kubota-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:54.68,0:32:55.17,Main,,0,0,0,,Here!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:55.17,0:32:57.93,Main,,0,0,0,,Hey! This is the graduation\Nalbum from Jr. High!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:59.34,0:33:00.82,Main,,0,0,0,,Nostalgic, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:00.82,0:33:05.76,Main,,0,0,0,,After I saw you, I felt like looking at it,\Nand went searching all over for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:06.95,0:33:08.82,Main,,0,0,0,,This is Fujisaki-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:09.45,0:33:12.45,Main,,0,0,0,,And in the front row, the small and\Ncute one, is Kobota-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:12.63,0:33:15.61,Main,,0,0,0,,Both of us have changed a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:15.61,0:33:16.73,Main,,0,0,0,,That's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:17.03,0:33:21.32,Main,,0,0,0,,After I entered high school,\NI grew about 20 centimeters.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:21.32,0:33:25.85,Main,,0,0,0,,That's why, after seeing you in Roppongi,\NI couldn't tell whether or not it was you.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:25.85,0:33:28.97,Main,,0,0,0,,Yea, I was hurt\Nthat you didn't say anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:28.97,0:33:30.90,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:31.47,0:33:35.24,Main,,0,0,0,,Say, do you remember what I said\Ntwo days ago, that night?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:35.24,0:33:38.98,Main,,0,0,0,,That I knew\Nyour feelings since Jr. high?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:38.98,0:33:42.61,Main,,0,0,0,,That's why, when you\Ndefended me at the disco,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:42.61,0:33:44.48,Main,,0,0,0,,I thought you might\Nstill have those feelings.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:45.25,0:33:46.59,Main,,0,0,0,,I...\N
Dialogue: 0,0:33:48.82,0:33:50.20,Main,,0,0,0,,...must be a cruel woman...
Dialogue: 0,0:34:00.61,0:34:03.23,Main,,0,0,0,,Fujisaki-san,\Nis it okay if I ask a question?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:03.23,0:34:04.43,Main,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:04.60,0:34:07.21,Main,,0,0,0,,Why is it that if it weren't\Ntoday, you wouldn't like it?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:07.69,0:34:10.80,Main,,0,0,0,,To me, everything seems rushed.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:15.51,0:34:20.60,Main,,0,0,0,,Faster, the quicker I can love you...
Dialogue: 0,0:34:22.94,0:34:25.82,Main,,0,0,0,,Kubota, I love you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:31.11,0:34:33.32,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh! I'm sorry! \NCould you wait a minute...?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:38.84,0:34:39.80,Main,,0,0,0,,Kazuya!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:41.61,0:34:42.80,Main,,0,0,0,,What's up?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:47.98,0:34:49.81,Main,,0,0,0,,What are you doing here,\Nat this time of night?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:49.81,0:34:53.32,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh, you're busy.  It seems\NI came at a bad time...
Dialogue: 0,0:35:01.01,0:35:04.83,Main,,0,0,0,,Don't look at me with those eyes.\NI just came to pick up some things I left.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:07.40,0:35:09.00,Main,,0,0,0,,Stuff you left?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:09.87,0:35:10.97,Main,,0,0,0,,Fujisaki-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:35:10.97,0:35:14.71,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, Kubota-kun.\NCan you sit over there and wait?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:20.21,0:35:22.81,Main,,0,0,0,,Fujisaki-san, did you live together?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:27.65,0:35:30.53,Main,,0,0,0,,Well, now we're even.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:31.80,0:35:36.74,Main,,0,0,0,,It looks like I'm \Nnot the only bad one.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:38.33,0:35:41.13,Main,,0,0,0,,Us living together was wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:41.80,0:35:45.20,Main,,0,0,0,,I didn't know you were\Nsuch a possessive woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:47.00,0:35:50.47,Main,,0,0,0,,You over there, I'm gonna\Ngive you a good piece of advice.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:50.47,0:35:55.05,Main,,0,0,0,,Masana may have a pretty face,\Nbut she likes to do this.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:55.05,0:35:56.09,Main,,0,0,0,,If you're not careful...
Dialogue: 0,0:35:58.60,0:36:03.31,Main,,0,0,0,,Let go. You and \NI have nothing to fight over.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:03.31,0:36:04.58,Main,,0,0,0,,Why you!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:04.58,0:36:07.36,Main,,0,0,0,,Kubota-kun please, stop! Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:24.44,0:36:26.79,Main,,0,0,0,,Kubota-kun, I...
Dialogue: 0,0:36:26.79,0:36:29.16,Main,,0,0,0,,That was Kawahara, wasn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:30.67,0:36:36.12,Main,,0,0,0,,Obviously, he's a horrible guy. All the\Nthings those girls said at the disco are true.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:36.12,0:36:37.45,Main,,0,0,0,,No, they're not!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:39.80,0:36:42.99,Main,,0,0,0,,He's just a big showoff.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:43.37,0:36:50.10,Main,,0,0,0,,I know... I know that he really is\Na pure person.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:51.30,0:36:55.71,Main,,0,0,0,,I know... I know that he really is\Na pure person.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:02.81,0:37:03.87,Main,,0,0,0,,That's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:08.72,0:37:14.45,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry. I can't be with a\Nperson whom looks at others too.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:18.53,0:37:23.33,Main,,0,0,0,,Fujisaki-san, please say something.\NOtherwise, all of this will be...
Dialogue: 0,0:37:25.22,0:37:26.30,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:54.82,0:38:55.49,Main,,0,0,0,,Yo!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:03.88,0:39:06.65,Main,,0,0,0,,Kazushi, don't be disappointed!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:07.11,0:39:10.14,Main,,0,0,0,,Next time, you'll find a\Nbetter girl than Fujisaki.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:10.51,0:39:12.85,Main,,0,0,0,,This cake isn't very sweet...
Dialogue: 0,0:39:14.36,0:39:19.55,Main,,0,0,0,,Kazushi, even though he seems great,\Ndid you know he's still a virgin?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:19.55,0:39:20.73,Main,,0,0,0,,Eh?!?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:20.73,0:39:21.65,Main,,0,0,0,,Why you...!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:21.65,0:39:26.16,Main,,0,0,0,,Hey! That's dangerous!\NStop that! Watch it!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:26.16,0:39:29.13,Main,,0,0,0,,We're safe! We're...okay!
